ActTerritorial Lands Act
PrecisREGULATIONS AMENDING AND REPEALING CERTAIN DEPARTMENT OF INDIAN AFFAIRS AND NORTHERN DEVELOPMENT REGULATIONS (MISCELLANEOUS PROGRAM) which remove all references to the Yukon Territory from the Canada Mining Regulations and the Territorial Land Use Regulations and repeal the Yukon Timber Regulations and the Yukon Forest Protection Regulations, effective April 1, 2003.
